Mobile Sample Data (Sample)

This notebook contains various chart examples based on a sample mobile phone dataset.

  • Note, this dataset joins the mobile sample table and the country codes.
  • Notice that the country names do not match completely hence the use of the case statement within the join.

select m.ClientID, c.CountryCode3, m.DeviceMake 
from mobile_sample m 
   join countrycodes c 
      on m.Country = c.Country
